Won't be &quot;uber&quot; for you damage-wise, but with the damage cap under level 20 I think a  sword that gives 15 ac and good stats and saves would be a nice pickup for a lower level paladin. They are sold on Terris Thule for 1k, and I see them for sale often.<br>
<br>
As others have said, any of the vanilla DN weapons would be good pickups, but I like my weapons to be more than just good damage and delay. <p>"Is it always the King who hangs?"
